data.description: Better than new! Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom single story home with two-car garage in the highly desired community of Paloma. This home is loaded with extra features which include Rinnai tankless water heater, water softener, rain gutters w/downspouts, water filter underneath kitchen sink, security system and Solar Panel roof.  Upon entering, guests are greeted by a lovely foyer that opens up to the main living area. The gorgeous kitchen overlooks the family room. The grand master suite is nestled in the corner of the home for optimum privacy and boasts a spacious owner's bath. Home includes window blinds and screens.  Fenced in the backyard is great for relaxing and entertaining with an extended / large back patio, beautiful landscaping and sprinkler system throughout.  Home also comes with a Tuff shed for additional storage. Easy commute to San Antonio and access to Selma where the Forum is located which has multiple restaurants and shopping centers!
